<p>
<note n="0136001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0136001">羅馬字本雖有十六行相，而舉十七。底本是十七行相。</note>
<note n="0137002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0137002">從羅馬字本。</note>
<note n="0138003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0138003">底本 muddhato 如羅馬字本改為 muddāto。</note>
<note n="0140004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0140004">ekaṁ Buddhasaranagataṁ satiṁ 羅馬字本為 ekaṁ Buddhagataṁ satiṁ。</note>
<note n="0141005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0141005">此偈頌羅馬字本無。</note>
<note n="0142006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0142006">羅馬字本否定，於底本以下之情形亦皆肯定。</note>
<note n="0146007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0146007">底本為 Kasmīranagara，省略 nagara。</note>
<note n="0146008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0146008">Kālasira 羅馬字本為 Kalasi。</note>
<note n="0148009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0148009">此譬喻羅馬字本無。</note>
<note n="0148010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0148010">此節羅馬字本無。</note>
<note n="0148011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0148011">速行事（turitakāraṇa）言受前二節之文而往他界之速。</note>
<note n="0153012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0153012">此節羅馬字本無。</note>
<note n="0155013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0155013">底本 vipakam gacchissati 依羅馬字本改為 vinipātaiṁ na gacchissati。</note>
<note n="0159014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0159014">將海（samudda）作為 sama（等）與 uda（水）之合成為俗解。</note>
<note n="0160015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0160015">與此幾乎同文出第六品第八。羅馬字本此處不出。</note>
<note n="0161016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0161016">參照第三品第六。</note>
<note n="0164017" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0164017">底本出於難問偈之前。此處不出。羅馬字本無。</note>
</p>
